Hello Markus,

There was another bug in the wiki page. This line should work in logging.properties:

org.archive.modules.canonicalize.RulesCanonicalizationPolicy.level = FINER

I&#39;ve updated the page.

Can you verify with that logging enabled that your rules are not being applied?

Noah


