&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; The exception will be thrown when this line appears in the canonicalizationPolicySheet bean:
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;entry key=&#39;preparer.canonicalizationPolicy&#39; value=&#39;altCanonicalizationPolicy&#39;/&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; It seems like it doesnt matter what i write inside the altcaonicalizationPolicy bean. Just the fact that I try to use it throws an exception.
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Does anyone have an idea what might be the problem? Im searching two days now but cant find anything.
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Thanks in advance,
&gt;&gt;&gt; Markus
